# 🍔 CraveCart - Food Ordering Platform

CraveCart is a modern food ordering web application inspired by food delivery platforms. Users can browse restaurants, view food items, add dishes to cart, place orders, and use a smart food assistant to get food suggestions based on mood, budget, and preferences.

## Live Demo

Add your GitHub Pages link here.

## Features

- Restaurant listing
- Food item cards
- Search functionality
- Add to cart
- Remove from cart
- Order placement
- AI-style food suggestion assistant
- Responsive modern UI

## Tech Stack

- HTML
- CSS
- JavaScript

